dct_title_s: Map showing the levelling from the Mediterranean to the Dead Sea
dct_description_sm: Relief shown by hachures and spot heights. From: the Journal of the Royal Geographical Society of London. Vol. 36, (1866), pp. 201-203; held in Firestone Library. Call number: G7 .J687 vol.36 1866. Includes elevation profile: "Section on the line levelled from the Mediterranean to the Dead Sea (the vertical scale is 8 times larger than the horizontal)".
dct_publisher_sm: London : published for the Journal of the Royal Geographical Society, by J. Murray, Albemarle Street, 1866.
